{{- /* mbsync (isync): pull Purelymail into a local Maildir for neomutt.
     Password from 1Password at apply time — no OAuth needed (Purelymail is plain IMAP).
     Referenced by ITEM ID, not title: two items are both titled "Purelymail"
     (two different mailboxes), so a title ref is ambiguous. */ -}}
IMAPAccount purelymail
Host imap.purelymail.com
Port 993
User {{ .email }}
Pass {{ onepasswordRead "op://Private/n44twyvw55ve5r5oy56i2gxmce/password" | quote }}
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2 +1.3
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore purelymail-remote
Account purelymail

MaildirStore purelymail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/purelymail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/purelymail/INBOX

Channel purelymail
Far :purelymail-remote:
Near :purelymail-local:
Patterns * !Trash !Spam !Junk
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
